body: Mid-Level implementation for LCDUI.
name: MLE UI LCDUI Forms [0.4.0]

body: **AutumnCoat** -- Compiler from register code to summercoat/x86/x86_64 machine code. Used as a practice to learn the ins and outs of it before WinterCoat. Allow for a general compilation engine that would still work to target SummerCoat, basically redone from what I have learned. Would initially target SummerCoat.
name: Mid-Level AutumnCoat [0.6.0/0.8.0]

body:
VBA Port of SquirrelJME.

April 1st, 2022??
name: BlockyCoat (SummerCoat/VBA) [2022]

body:
Support for multiple different graphics formats and drawing for those. Will be using class templates.

The resultant of this project should result in faster drawing operations without requiring any memory (or some depending on the situation but cached).
name: Generic Multi-Format Graphics [0.4.0]

body:
Implementation of the various UI Forms on top of a basic framebuffer, this will be for when native forms are not supported for a system.

The style will emulate Mac OS Classic, with an orange/pink/blue theme.
name: Framebuffer UI Forms [0.4.0]
